{
  "stem": "2316.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians helped them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we watched it burn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the flames-- it was just like watching the Civil War in Atlanta when was made.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was incredible, those flames.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'll never forget it as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just terrible for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was my home, my kids, my school, my toys, whatever, my doll, everything went up in-- the whole city, everything that meant anything to me went up in flames.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I will never forget those-- those flames.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were miles, miles high, and smoke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the smell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The-- all the woods in the entire world smelled with smoke that night and that day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was-- I've never seen such fires.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I've never seen anything like it, even in the movies during wars that I witnessed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I mean, to see our whole town burning-- your town, your home, you know, that's like the end of you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There's no one way-- there's no way ever see life again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so there was no shtetl to come back to, so we went to the next shtetl, which was called Kiwerce.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It wasn't far from Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And a few survivors, like my cousins that were hiding out with us, came there, and some other survivors, and a few more people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We lived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And at that time, the Russians were, of course, already came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Russians [? took. ?] It was the end of the war, and so the Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I don't remember what they did, how they made a living, but they worked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember the government gave them jobs or public offices and factories, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The men started to work, and we started to eat food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, it was something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
